- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category because Markov decision processes are commonly used in AI for decision-making problems. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category because Markov decision processes are used in reinforcement learning, a subfield of machine learning. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a possible category because Markov decision processes are used in game theory for modeling decision-making in games.
